# Sūra XXVI.: Shu‘arāa, or The Poets.

### Section 1

![](../gif/026/026_001.gif)

1. <u>Ta</u>-seen-meem

1\. Tā. Sīn. Mīm.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_002.gif)

2. Tilka <u>a</u>y<u>a</u>tu alkit<u>a</u>bi almubeen**i**

2\. These are Verses of the Book  
That makes (things) clear.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_003.gif)

3. LaAAallaka b<u>a</u>khiAAun nafsaka all<u>a</u> yakoonoo
mu/mineen**a**

3\. It may be thou frettest  
Thy soul with grief, that they  
Do not become Believers.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_004.gif)

4. In nasha/ nunazzil AAalayhim mina a**l**ssam<u>a</u>-i <u>a</u>yatan
fa*<u>th</u>*allat aAAn<u>a</u>quhum lah<u>a</u> kh<u>ad</u>iAAeen**a**

4\. If (such) were Our Will,  
We could send down to them  
From the sky a Sign,  
To which they would bend  
Their necks in humility.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_005.gif)

5. Wam<u>a</u> ya/teehim min <u>th</u>ikrin mina
a**l**rra<u>h</u>m<u>a</u>ni mu<u>h</u>dathin ill<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>noo
AAanhu muAAri<u>d</u>een**a**

5\. But there comes not  
To them a newly-revealed  
Message from (God) Most Gracious,  
But they turn away therefrom.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_006.gif)

6. Faqad ka<u>thth</u>aboo fasaya/teehim anb<u>a</u>o m<u>a</u>
k<u>a</u>noo bihi yastahzi-oon**a**

6\. They have indeed rejected  
(The Message): so they will  
Know soon (enough) the truth  
Of what they mocked at!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_007.gif)

7. Awa lam yaraw il<u>a</u> al-ar<u>d</u>i kam anbatn<u>a</u>
feeh<u>a</u> min kulli zawjin kareem**in**

7\. Do they not look  
At the earth,—how many  
Noble things of all kinds  
We have produced therein?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_008.gif)

8. Inna fee <u>tha</u>lika la<u>a</u>yatan wam<u>a</u> k<u>a</u>na
aktharuhum mu/mineen**a**

8\. Verily, in this is a Sign:  
But most of them  
Do not believe.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/026/026_009.gif)

9. Wa-inna rabbaka lahuwa alAAazeezu a**l**rra<u>h</u>eem**u**

9\. And verily, thy Lord  
Is He, the Exalted in Might,  
Most Merciful.

